high_descs: Turn around, walk straight and reach the countertop sink.
Pick up the bowl from the kitchen countertop.
Put the bowl in to the wash basin.
Open the water tab and clean the bowl and Take back the bowl from sink
Move across the room and go to the kitchen countertop.
Place the bowl on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the clean Bowl on the kitchen CounterTop

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the kitchen countertop.
Pick the wooden bowl from the kitchen counter top.
Open the tap and wash the bowl in the sink.
Take it and turn around towards the countertop.
Place the bowl on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Wash and place the Bowl on the CounterTop

high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen countertop to the left of the sink.
Pick up the bowl from the kitchen counter to the left of the sink.
Walk over to the kitchen counter near the kitchen sink faucet.
Place the bowl into the kitchen sink under the faucet, turn the water on then off, and pick up the bowl from the sink.
Walk slightly over to the kitchen countertop to the left of the sink.
Place the bowl on the front corner of the countertop to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Wash a bowl in the kitchen sink to return to the kitchen countertop.
